    <item>
      <title>若欧洲央行降低法国债券收益率，德国可能表示反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-may-object-if-ecb-moves-to-lower-french-bond-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 表示，如果法国立法选举引发该国政府债券的危险抛售，欧洲央行的干预可能是非法的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-may-object-if-ecb-moves-to-lower-french-bond-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:21:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士扩大与美国银行数据共享 打击逃税行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/swiss-widen-bank-data-sharing-with-us-in-tax-dodging-clampdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士和美国已加强银行信息的自动交换，这使得美国公民更难以阻止自己的账户数据落入美国税务机关的手中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/swiss-widen-bank-data-sharing-with-us-in-tax-dodging-clampdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:16:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国、波兰要求欧盟帮助支付收容乌克兰难民的费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-poland-ask-eu-to-help-pay-for-hosting-ukraine-refugees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国、波兰和捷克共和国请求欧盟提供资金援助，以帮助支付接收乌克兰难民的费用，因为自俄罗斯入侵以来，这三个国家接收了大部分难民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-poland-ask-eu-to-help-pay-for-hosting-ukraine-refugees</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:38:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国大选后工党获得数十亿美元私人投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/labour-expects-billions-of-private-investment-after-uk-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 计划在工党执政的头几个月内在英国引入价值数十亿英镑的新私人投资 —— 反对党希望这笔投资足以实现其雄心勃勃的增长目标，并在赢得下周的选举后避免增税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/labour-expects-billions-of-private-investment-after-uk-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波士顿写字楼市场低迷给居民带来 4 亿美元负担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/boston-office-slump-forces-choice-on-higher-taxes-400-million-budget-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿市长米歇尔吴在接受彭博新闻社采访时表示，如果州议员拒绝将负担转移到商业建筑的计划，波士顿居民将面临房产税大幅上涨或面临 4 亿美元预算削减的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/boston-office-slump-forces-choice-on-higher-taxes-400-million-budget-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:25:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非国大撤回贸易提议后南非内阁谈判陷入僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/south-africa-cabinet-talks-stall-after-anc-withdraws-trade-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，南非非洲人国民大会撤回了任命规模较小的民主联盟成员担任贸易和工业部长的提议，此后南非两大政党之间组建内阁的谈判陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/south-africa-cabinet-talks-stall-after-anc-withdraws-trade-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内阁会议拖延令投资者担忧，南非股市抛售加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/rand-resumes-losses-as-south-africa-cabinet-delay-fuels-angst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非选举结果所激发的乐观情绪正在消退，因为总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 新内阁组建延迟，令投资者担心这将在多大程度上削弱他们所期待的市场友好型政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/rand-resumes-losses-as-south-africa-cabinet-delay-fuels-angst</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:15:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前特朗普助手菲利克斯·萨特洗钱案败诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/ex-trump-associate-felix-sater-loses-ny-money-laundering-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费利克斯·萨特（Felix Sater）是一位出生于莫斯科的交易员，曾是唐纳德·特朗普的核心圈子成员，他在一场民事审判中败诉，他被指控帮助一名富有的哈萨克斯坦男子通过美国房地产（包括特朗普 SoHo 大厦的公寓）洗钱数百万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/ex-trump-associate-felix-sater-loses-ny-money-laundering-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:24:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>疫情援助收益到期后，芝加哥寻求收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/chicago-hunts-for-more-revenue-as-gains-from-pandemic-aid-expire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥领导人发起了一场可能很棘手的讨论，重点是如何在未来几年联邦疫情援助逐渐减少的情况下增加收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/chicago-hunts-for-more-revenue-as-gains-from-pandemic-aid-expire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 22:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>圣保罗水务公司股份出售仅吸引一名竞标者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/sao-paulo-water-utility-s-privization-said-to-lure-single-bidder</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西电力公司赤道能源公司 (Equatorial Energia SA) 成为竞购 Sabesp 关键股权的唯一竞标者，Sabesp 是一家水务公司，圣保罗州将通过数十亿美元的股票发行将其私有化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/sao-paulo-water-utility-s-privization-said-to-lure-single-bidder</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 22:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
